{{define "content"}}
<div class="static-page privacy-page">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    {{if .Config.Server.Pages.Privacy.Content}}
    <div class="page-content markdown">
        {{.Config.Server.Pages.Privacy.Content | safe}}
    </div>
    {{else}}
    <div class="page-content">
        <section class="privacy-section">
            <h2>Data Collection</h2>
            <p>{{.Config.Server.Branding.AppName}} is designed with privacy as a core principle. We minimize data collection to what is strictly necessary for the service to function.</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Search Queries:</strong> Your search queries are sent to upstream search engines but are not stored on our servers.</li>
                <li><strong>IP Addresses:</strong> We do not log IP addresses or use them for tracking.</li>
                <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> We only use essential cookies for session management and user preferences (like theme settings).</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-section">
            <h2>Data Usage</h2>
            <p>Any data that is temporarily processed is used only to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Forward your search query to upstream search engines</li>
                <li>Aggregate and display results to you</li>
                <li>Remember your preferences (theme, language)</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-section">
            <h2>Data Retention</h2>
            <p>We do not retain search queries or personal data. Session data is temporary and is deleted when you close your browser or your session expires.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-section">
            <h2>Third Parties</h2>
            <p>Your search queries are forwarded to upstream search engines to retrieve results. We do not share any other data with third parties.</p>
            <p>Each upstream search engine has its own privacy policy. We recommend reviewing them if you have concerns.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-section">
            <h2>Cookies</h2>
            <p>We use only essential cookies:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Session Cookie:</strong> To maintain your session (if logged in)</li>
                <li><strong>Preference Cookie:</strong> To remember your theme and language preferences</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We do not use tracking cookies, analytics cookies, or advertising cookies.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-section">
            <h2>Your Rights</h2>
            <p>Since we don't store personal data, there is no data to access, modify, or delete. Your privacy is protected by design.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-section">
            <h2>Contact</h2>
            <p>If you have questions about our privacy practices, please <a href="/server/contact">contact us</a>.</p>
        </section>
    </div>
    {{end}}
</div>
{{end}}
